name: E.T.H.O.S. EPISODE #1
description:
a bored ape awakens on a new timeline to find himself in a conversation with a trash mystic and a talking gorilla. 

he can only stay in the micro-home for a while… it’s being auctioned off. 

surrounded by chickens, he contemplates his next move. 

29 second video collage art | collaborative piece by Art Is Solidarity genesis artists | SolidarityArt.org |
